{"tid":2247724,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【召喚大和田】西方學者指中国在非洲監視及竊聽西方國家","createTime":"2020-10-18T05:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T07:30:09.000Z","uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a00de6c387737fb523f6e5c05a58ab496a3d7abc","tid":2247724,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"被指利用基建在非洲監聽 華使館斥西方以己度人<br />\n<br />\n近日有西方學者批評，中國在非洲修建不少政府建築，旨在通過這些設施監視西方國家。中國駐加納大使館周日（18日）引述評論文章，駁斥中國在非洲「搞竊聽」的說法，強調散播仇視中國的無知言論只會進一步加強中非合作。<br />\n<br />\n有西方學者指摘中國利用基建在非洲進行監聽活動，中方在非洲修建政府建築是為了通過這些設施獲取情報，監聽西方國家，並影響非洲官員，為中國企業爭取競爭優勢等。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐加納大使館引述當地傳媒近日刊登的評論文章《中非關係展望》，駁斥上述言論毫無根據，反指西方國家長期監控非洲國家政府，以鞏固在非洲及全球的影響力，故以己度人，認為中國會這樣做。華使館強調，中國視非洲為朋友而非敵人，兩地關係發展並沒損害非洲利益，但可能損害與中國同在非洲競爭國家的利益；反斥有些國家希望非洲繼續落後，在經濟上依賴他們。"},{"pid":"127caf1ed084ee0ced7f6bf7d3f2df8625bd6ebd","tid":2247724,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201018/mobile/bkn-20201018100112330-1018_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20201018%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201018100112330-1018_00952_001.html&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=da7e9b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201018/mobile/bkn-20201018100112330-1018_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"405841ff197bbc137ab452c9e6afd9960fa41717","tid":2247724,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cZHiQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cZHiQY.gif&h=1855717c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8tpxa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8tpxa3.gif&h=a7b8cd54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef15abb6deb26a62b70ef3b6b6871b8fa05960ce","tid":2247724,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"405841ff197bbc137ab452c9e6afd9960fa41717","tid":2247724,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cZHiQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cZHiQY.gif&h=1855717c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8tpxa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8tpxa3.gif&h=a7b8cd54&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"又有新圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260890513843bfdfa354d139b7d801bc237c3f4b","tid":2247724,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"你寧願比西方監聽定比中國監聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc946f253915f61e5290897d66b26e5a9bcda4f3","tid":2247724,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"我突然諗起condom 香港前局長 眼科醫生肥平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}